caption: On the wall of the Shoah memorial inaugurated on 06/14/2006, plaques pay tribute to the Justrs of France. Place filled with emotions never to be forgotten.

A few steps in front of this wall, thinking of this time when, in the chaos, men and women "like everyone else" defended the oppressed, protected children from certain death, allowed France to have today with my head held high. Respect !

Place of recognition for people who helped Jews in France during World War II. Also, exhibition on genocides around the world. Interesting visit, it makes you reflect and realize how important it is to know history. Highly recommended.

When I found my father's name I couldn't hold back my emotion⁰ trrrerrible The writing workshop was in fact a workshop on the Holocaust, I am looking for a real one Anne Frank Simone Weill hover over this extraordinary place with the 6 million massacred because of roots Dramatic
Very moving place. The duty to remember is essential.
